text: int main ( ) { int i , n , a , b , lcm , gcd ; scanf ( "%d" , & n ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= n ; i ++ ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; { for ( i = 1 ; i <= a && i <= b ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) gcd = i ; } } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
